replies.body:
I agree with you completely.

If riot added a sandbox mode. It would mean that you would be spending less time to master a champion because you could just work out the certain kinks in your play. By having to where you would have to play tons of games just to master a certain champ/role/mechanic you play more. They don't want you playing a little and getting a lot of results. They want you playing as much as possible while making just enough progress to keep you playing. By having a sandbox you get better quicker meaning less play time{{champion:1}} 

Also side note to rito you didn't explain why having a sandbox would be bad. You just said that you didn't think was a direction that should be taken.
